content:
This error usually occurs when the necessary package is not imported or defined in the preamble. In this case, it could be a missing package that provides the `\includegraphics` command. Make sure to add the following line to the preamble of your LaTeX document:
```
\usepackage{graphicx}
```
This package provides the `\includegraphics` command which is used to insert images in LaTeX documents. Once this package is imported, the error should be resolved.
